1: Decrease Hit Points (HP) from 42 (L12) to 44 (L16)<br>
Classes: Wiz (L12)<br>
<br>
Skill: Evocation<br>
Allowable Targets: Target Based AoE<br>
Beneficial: Detrimental<br>
Range to Target: 200.00 feet<br>
Area Effect Range: 35.00 feet<br>
Resistance Check: Cold<br>
Base Difficulty: 25%<br>
Mana Cost: 100<br>
Spell Duration: Instant<br>
Area Effect Duration: 5<br>
Casting Time: 3.15 seconds<br>
Spell Recovery: 2.50 seconds<br>
Recast Delay: 9.0 seconds<br>
<br>
Spell cast on you: You are blasted by freezing winds.<br>
Spell cast on someone: An orc centurion is blasted by freezing winds.<br>
<br>
